half a grapefruit please.

16:23.350 --> 16:24.582
And the smallest scone
you got.

16:24.584 --> 16:25.817
Alright.

16:27.921 --> 16:29.854
So, what's it been, Jim?
A couple of months?

16:29.856 --> 16:30.989
