31:49.074 --> 31:51.341
- Hm. Alright.
- A little. Yeah. Just a sliver.

31:51.343 --> 31:53.343
- Entitled?
- Yeah, yeah.

31:53.345 --> 31:54.711
Well, you see it's pretty
simple, Jim.

31:54.713 --> 31:56.747
