you forgot

32:25.477 --> 32:26.910
what you're supposed
to be doing here.

32:26.912 --> 32:29.146
I need less champagne...

32:29.148 --> 32:31.248
- More cocaine.
- That's clever, you know.

32:31.250 --> 32:33.417
And if you've got some sort of
misplaced loyalty

32:33.419 --> 32:35.585
to Morgan or you think
you're protecting your family

32:35.587 --> 32:38.555
by fucking this shit up,
you're sadly fuckin' mistaken.

32:38.557 --> 32:39.923
