pay you ten percent.

32:46.398 --> 32:49.032
You owe us. We don't owe you.

32:51.136 --> 32:53.804
Your next check
is gonna be short a 126 bucks,

32:53.806 --> 32:56.340
because that's how much
those wires cost.

32:56.342 --> 32:58.508
Hey.

32:58.510 --> 33:00.711
I could probably get you a
better deal on those, you know?

33:08.153 --> 33:10.654
[upbeat music]

33:11.790 --> 33:13.991
[children shouting]

33:19.965 --> 33:21.999
Hey, that's a groovy little
camera you got.

33:22.001 --> 33:23.467
- Hello.
- Betamax, man.

33:23.469 --> 33:25.202
Uh-huh.

33:25.204 --> 33:26.703
Any money you're not putting
into DeLorean,

33:26.705 --> 33:28.005
put it into Betamax.

33:28.007 --> 33:29.406
What money?

33:31.977 --> 33:33.844
I don't know
why she bothers with him.

33:36.181 --> 33:38.648
You know, he's chained
by a grandmaster.

33:38.650 --> 33:39.883
Really?

33:41.220 --> 33:42.619
Oh.

33:50.529 --> 33:53.964
James Hoffman.
What is that German?

33:53.966 --> 33:55.399
Yeah, I guess so.

33:55.401 --> 33:57.667
You know, Jim,
everything is out there.

33:57.669 --> 33:59.302
It just takes a bit of leg work.

33:59.304 --> 34:00.470
But that's what I do.

34:02.241 --> 34:04.908
I gotta say,
most people are kinda straight.

34:04.910 --> 34:07.344
But every once in a while,
you come up against someone

34:07.346 --> 34:10.047
who's just 90% bullshit.

34:11.016 --> 34:12.582
Wants to hitch a ride.

34:14.086 --> 34:16.853
The thing is, I haven't been
able to turn up

34:16.855 --> 34:18.288
anything about you at all.

34:20.025 --> 34:21.258
That worries me.

34:23.395 --> 34:25.395
Yeah, that worries me too,
actually.

34:26.031 --> 34:27.464
Oh.

34:29.268 --> 34:31.835
- Hey, Ellen.
- Yeah?

34:31.837 --> 34:34.838
Roy here thinks
I'm 90% bullshit.

34:34.840 --> 34:36.006
Ninety?

34:36.008 --> 34:38.909
