Fuck them and fuck their marble.

39:22.561 --> 39:24.461
What... What're you
talkin' about? Who? Who? Who?

39:24.463 --> 39:25.962
- What's wrong?
- John and Cristina.

39:25.964 --> 39:28.031
It's marble this
and marble that.

39:28.033 --> 39:29.999
- Why don't we have any marble?
- Hey! Hey! Hey!

39:30.001 --> 39:31.501
What are you doing? Come here.
