like that.

40:27.759 --> 40:30.059
John: Why not? It's my money.
Molly: No, it's not.

40:30.061 --> 40:31.461
Molly: Christ, John.
If someone finds out--

40:31.463 --> 40:34.097
John: Well, that's why
we're switching...

40:35.133 --> 40:36.366
Jim.

40:37.135 --> 40:38.368
Ellen: Jim!

40:39.438 --> 40:40.637
What?

40:41.640 --> 40:44.207
Ellen: Hurry! Hurry! Quick.

40:44.209 --> 40:46.409
- Jim, come here. Look.
- What's goin' on?

40:46.411 --> 40:48.445
I think it's clear
what's going on.

40:50.282 --> 40:52.081
Jim: Oh, come on.

40:52.083 --> 40:53.783
They work together.

40:53.785 --> 40:54.984
Ellen: Something's going on.

40:54.986 --> 40:56.319
He's just trying
to calm her down.

40:56.321 --> 40:57.954
I-- I don't know
what the big deal is.

40:57.956 --> 40:59.889
Oh, my God, you think
you're so good with people,

40:59.891 --> 41:02.926
