41:27.786 --> 41:29.986
- Really?
- Think about...

41:29.988 --> 41:32.322
- Hey, uh, I better go, okay?
- What is that?

41:32.324 --> 41:33.590
What time are you
pickin' up the kids from school?

41:33.592 --> 41:35.024
- Baby! Baby!
- It's a button.

41:35.026 --> 41:37.627
What is that? No, no, no, no!
This... [gasps]

41:37.629 --> 41:39.796
- What the fuck?
- It's just a gadget that...

41:39.798 --> 41:42.098
- Oh, shit! Okay--
- What is going on?

41:42.100 --> 41:43.633
